    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "RE: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "Your attention is directed to Bureau Bulletin #57, Series 1947, dated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "October 1, 1947, relating to the discontinuance of investigation by this Bureau in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "matters concerning flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "For your confidential information, a reliable and confidential source",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "has advised the Bureau that flying discs are believed to be man-made missiles rather",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "than natural phenomenon. It has also been determined that for approximately the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "past four years the USSR has been engaged in experimentation on an unknown type",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "of flying disc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "The Department of the Air Force has furnished to the Bureau the attached",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "memorandum classified \"restricted\" dated February 15, 1949, entitled \"Unconventional",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "Aircraft.\" This memorandum is being furnished to you in order that all agents",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "assigned to your office can be informed of the type of information desired by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "Air Force in this matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "As set forth in Bureau Bulletin #57, referred to above, no investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "should be conducted by your office relative to flying discs, however, the attached",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "memorandum should be referred to in securing data from persons who desire to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "voluntarily furnish information to your office relating to flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "Very truly yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "status": "blank"
    },
